title: Bitwise CIO Predicts Bitcoin Bull Market Won’t End Early — Expects an ‘Everything Season’
description: The chief investment officer at Bitwise Asset Management has explained why the current bitcoin bull market differs from prior bull markets. He doesn’t expect the bull market or the alts season to “end early,” emphasizing that he expects to see “more of an ‘everything season,'” rather than a classic alts season.
